==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Boating
<hw>Boat"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act or practice of
rowing or sailing, esp. as an amusement; carriage in boats.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>In Persia, a punishment of capital offenders, by
laying them on the back in a covered boat, where they are left to
perish.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Boation</ent>⟦br⟧
